<title>UK: ICI says has no plans for rights issue.</title>
<headline>ICI says has no plans for rights issue.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-02-06</dateline>
<text>
<p>Imperial Chemical Industries Plc said on Thursday that it had no plans for a rights issue.</p>
<p>Asked about recent speculation that the group was planning a rights issue to fund a major paints acquisition in Europe, ICI chairman Sir Ronald Hampel said: &quot;No&quot;.</p>
<p>Hampel, speaking at a news briefing following the group's 1996 results, reiterated ICI's intention of expanding its paints business through a mix of acquisition and volume growth.</p>
